description:
Current tags are: ;3, uwu

Optional tags: catmouth, smug

Don't use ":3", I didn't include it as a tag since :3 will fry any image.

No longer supports "open mouth", but you still may see some ok results with it by including catmouth and fiddling with the parameters.

0.6-0.8 scale usually works best.
